| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1770 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5ab35cc0-2fea-5d0c-8d2a-c2ced9fcc993"
